Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wai—Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was saying you should kiss Manaka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Either way, why should I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it could help her wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's a k-kiss got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I already explained it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not an explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't yell at girls like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's all 'cause she—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?{Hikari}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
