Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going out, Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She left in a pretty big hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna come...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only going out for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, don't push Manaka-chan too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't go dragging her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that habit of always running ahead of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she starts feeling tired or sick—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right{,} already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka-chan, make sure you ask Hikari to do whatever you need him to, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka, I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's been a while, so take your time{,} and have lots of fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, you're staying home with Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaka! I wanna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Namaka! Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Namaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure does like you a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.71,0:03:52.67,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.28\blur0.8\frz15.89\fscx145\fscy145\c&H3B0079&\1a&H55&\pos(980,273)}Saya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally together again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Four from Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great she woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't quite the same unless you guys are all together.{The four of you together are one unit.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, here's a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Mukaido I said hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There are five in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to have one left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan, it's cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other in so long, and {\i1}that's{\i0} the first thing you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really {\i1}is{\i0} cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's supposed to be summer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, normally{,} people would be more surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,especially considering how much some of us have grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan's the same as always, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu's not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to do field work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's on top of the ice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's busy, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see him another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, more importantly, \Nlet's all go to the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My body suddenly got all crackly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So when your Ena gets dried up, it gets crackly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's quite "crackly." It's also sort of hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time it's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it sounds like a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Hikari and everyone else \Ntell you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've just gone with them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari invited you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The right to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... the right to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you say that after you did all that research?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not happy Manaka-san woke up, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself, "She finally woke up,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was even happy that I was {actually }happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But something was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was different from how I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no clue what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.01,0:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I'm supposed to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see the look on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I don't have any Ena, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You could already see that from the house, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when you see it up close, \Nit's really surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.18,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boatdrift Ceremony was just the other day for you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the saltflake snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't this much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like playing "Spot the Difference" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Spot the Difference"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each time I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and then open them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spot things that are different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Saltflake snow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Saltflake snow there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saltflake snow {\i1}everywhere{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? You're only pointing out the saltflake snow, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Tehe.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun's being nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—I've always been nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun, your face is red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me, Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's saltflake snow over there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka, you shouldn't run like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It sort of makes you wonder why we tried so hard, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even without {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}'s help,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka woke up all on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, {in the end, }it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you could say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's sort of anticlimactic too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what with the way she's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's so full of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chii-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she only woke up yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you act, Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the town looked familiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,everything was just a little off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought to myself, "If everywhere looks the same, \Nbut I don't know a single person,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what am I going to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't take seeing any more things that have changed!{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna think about all of this!{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,475)}I don't even wanna know about 'em!{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get how she can laugh so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're here, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so are we.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was so sure she'd wanna go see {\i1}him{\i0} first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, she says she can't{kind of inaccurate but commonly used} remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:11.09,Chalk Pusher Is Pushing It,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\c&H3B2619&\frz2.918\1a&H3A&\fry180\fscx41\fscy36\pos(216,69)\blur4\t(0,1500,1,\blur0.6)}Wake up, Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:11.29,Chalk Pusher Is Pushing It,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&H000000&\frz2.918\fscx73\fscy65\pos(1013,10)\1a&H3A&\clip(m 892 0 l 980 83 1210 -15)}Wake up, Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.30,Chalk Pusher Is Pushing It,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&H000000&\frz2.918\fscx73\fscy65\pos(1013,10)\1a&H3A&}Wake up, Manaka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the Boatdrift Ceremony, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I mean, what happened after the Boatdrift Ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You got pulled down to the bottom of the sea. \NWhat happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I heard someone's voice—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose was it? Was it {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}'s?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}'s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the sea god?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he said he'd give me something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or he asked me to give him something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd he ask for?{An incorrect, uncommon contraction often used in speech.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Manaka, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}Even the school is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,covered in saltflake snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's so fluffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have Ena anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't ever go back to the sea now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can she be like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's still Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This side's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Okay, I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! You can't step on this side anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here, here, and here are all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,No! You can't have all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you at school on a Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking. What are {\i1}you{\i0} doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided to study for our exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know? Finals are next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to go and bring {\i1}that{\i0} up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying is important, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In math, we're learning about simultaneous equations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And in English, we're learning about conjunctions and verbal nouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm really bad at both of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, talk about a buzzkill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, besides simple arithmetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,math is pretty useless anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on cue, the excuse of a true idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wha?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm in total agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think studying is important too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hear that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying's important! Right, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's much better to study properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late to regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to start heading to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu's grandfather isn't well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's pretty old now, \Nand a lot has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I nearly forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayama-kun gave them to us.
