Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just enough for each of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki-san's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants one?
