Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We all want one!
