Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I had a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've gone to see Manaka, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that she might get overwhelmed if she saw too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get over how full of energy she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'd come visit us soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a tangerine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's coffee jelly in there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps remembered my two favorite foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I might like this even more than cream puffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring up cream puffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to head back to campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The university is getting on the professor's case to put together our data and conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When will that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said the end of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes really sour because I ate that sweet jelly first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to send tangerines to your apartment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat them with all the people in your lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that far, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll call, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I find some new information, I'll let you know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Tsumugu? You gonna be lonely?{"gonna" is rare for Chisaki in my editing, but I'm altering the way she speaks to Tsumugu specifically.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me I'm worried about. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll have to keep an eye on Manaka, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She can be so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka really hasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need to worry about such trivial things, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just focus on your research at your lab, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you and Professor Mihashi to figure all this out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still so much that we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Manaka woke up{,}{This comma would be for readability only.} and Hikari and Kaname seem fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so much we don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what will happen to the sea or the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{or to the world's future, }or to the weather or the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could ask {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}? Why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he seems to know \Neverything about the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling he'd just say something random and useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a scale of the sea god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't know if he'd tell us anything even if we found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always so perverse,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention {\i1}perverted{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could bribe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bribe him? With money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. Maybe with porn mags.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, that might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That really just might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't insist if you guys really can't come, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dadda! Where's Dadda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Akira, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dadda's working late tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you can't put the fish in like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. The flavor comes out better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd Tsumugu say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems neither of them can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No touching the crab, Akira. It's very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came up with Tsumugu's grandfather. They apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii-chan must be really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu is too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, both of {\i1}them{\i0} actually study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound like I don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You never study.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the entrance exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, maybe I should go and hibernate again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stupid things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu-chan, help Hikari with his studies, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're at the top of the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sometimes. It's {\i1}all{\i0} the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everyone's applying for Hama High School, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not as though \NShishio has a high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I like things the way \Nthey are {\i1}now{\i0}, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your crab, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow on it a lot before you eat it, okay?{wtf just happened?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still feel hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? It doesn't hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, guys. \NHe's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:20:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,477)}Is all this because the sea god is angry?{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you had something to tell me \Nafter the Boatdrift Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Boatdrift Ceremony...{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}I'll tell you when it's over.{PV}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it you were gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making such a scary face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it about Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Tsumugu, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... it's you, Tsumugu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I please talk to Mukaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's everyone doing up so—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu-kun, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was cursed by {replace}Uroko-sama{Lord Uroko}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the type of person \Nthat puts curses on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I dunno if I'd call him a "person."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But this means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uroko's somewhere close by.
